    "summary": "The user role portrays an individual experiencing existential dread and nihilistic ideation, questioning the point of existence in a vast, indifferent universe. The assistant role responds with standard, supportive, and empathetic language, attempting to steer the user toward finding meaning and emphasizing that they are not alone.",
